data.description: A slice of HEAVEN in the country with room for horses and ag projects and whatever your heart desires! 4.1+/- acres of fully-fenced level grassland loaded with wildlife and wildflowers (even wild watermelons!) with a single story 3 bedroom, 2 bath home with lovely updates and tons of sunny windows! Three eating areas throughout a light and bright open floorplan with all tile and LVP flooring (no carpet!) flows out to the huge covered back patio for easy-going sunsets, firepit time and barbeques. The gated entry to your country home is just down the road from Devine and local schools on a paved farm-to-market road. If you desire country privacy and useful space, bring your RV and your workshop projects because the property has a 50-amp RV hookup and a '20x40' concrete floor workshop with 20'x30' enclosed and a 10 ft overhang/carport. The workshop has multiple electrical circuits on their own breakers. There is also a separate wooden storage shed of approx 12x20. A fenced chicken coop with a water faucet for easy watering will convey and even includes a few chickens to make sure you have eggs immediately! Upgrades in the home include recent new doors, ceiling fans, granite, a breakfast bar and island kitchen, Kinetico Water Softener and so much more!
